2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Metric learning is a subfield of machine learning, and this paper evaluates the performance of metric learning algorithms. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Metric learning is also relevant to artificial intelligence, particularly in areas such as natural language processing and recommendation systems. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Metric learning is often used in multimedia applications such as image and video retrieval. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - Metric learning can also be applied to information retrieval tasks such as document similarity and recommendation systems.
